cc:Work.dc:title: Box - NotesHolder
cc:Work.dc:description:
Box for holding a stack of paper, coasters etc
If the feet of the `Stackable` `bottom_edge` don't fit on the front (and back) walls you can make them smaller by reducing `width` and/or increasing `angle` in the `Settings for Stackable Edges`. Reducing the `opening` will also give more space for the feet.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes NotesHolder Command line short: boxes NotesHolder
